{"tid":2232231,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港同台灣D大人物咁唔同","createTime":"2020-10-06T09:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T09:09:08.000Z","uid":39734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"60d2332d0fa0e342584b1f44a30a598b858bfcf0","tid":2232231,"uid":39734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:00:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qq_pAYVuZk4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dqq_pAYVuZk4&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=9216435e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qq_pAYVuZk4</a><br />\n<br />\n入面龍應台成日寫D好似好傳統既散文, 又一把年紀, 但係上鏡好得體, 又玩得, 識俾反應<br />\nD主持雖然都係夠時間要overrun, 但係都係幽默帶過, 唔會好似香港果隻鴨咁係咁講「夠鐘啦快D啦」, 仲有表演緊既時間又唔會成日插咀show off自己好叻(而最衰係唔叻)<br />\n<br />\n除左標準答案「特首唔同」之外, 點解可以爭咁遠?<br />\n人地D節目真係賞心悅目, 但香港TVB D節目俾人睇真係尷尬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99d440a58774ac80d4f1e0845b73d81e65bdd78","tid":2232231,"uid":39734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T09:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}